description:
&lt;p&gt;This is a very exciting opportunity to join the Orthopaedic MDT Team at Broadgreen Hospital site, Liverpool University Hospitals NHS FT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 7 is a newly created ward to provide support for the Orthopaedic changes that have occurred as part of the trust Merger&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will work as an integral part of the ward team ensuring a high quality service to our patients. This is a very exciting job and you will gain valuable experience while being part of a team striving for excellent care and patient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic, highly motivated and enthusiastic person to join our Multi-disciplinary team. The successful candidate will be able to demonstrate excellent communication skills, team working skills and dedicated to improving patient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to demonstrate continuing professional development and a strong commitment to develop others and work closely within a Multidisciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience in orthopaedics would be an advantage but not essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Newly qualified nurses will be considered. Support and excellent mentorship given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Broadgreen has excellent staff facilities and parking is available. The site is located close to the M62 and has excellent bus and train services nearby. It is a friendly site with excellent educational opportunities and support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal visits can be arranged.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
